T1  - Marketplace Scalability and Strategic Use of Platform Investment
AU  - Li, Jin
AU  - Pisano, Gary
AU  - Xu, Yejia
AU  - Zhu, Feng
Y1  - 2022/12/09
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2023/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4522
